{"title":"转向游戏","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":0,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-1512","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>小明自认为方向感很好，请小红来测试。小红先让小明面对北方立正站好，然后发出“向左转”“向右转”或“向后转”的命令。每个命令执行后，小明都正确地说出了他面对的方向。小红的命令共N个(1≤n≤10000)，请你统计小明说【南】的次数。</p>\n<p>命令是以数字方式表达：</p>\n<p>0---向左转</p>\n<p>1---向右转</p>\n<p>2---向后转</p>\n<p>如小红发出的5个命令：0 1 0 0 1 ；小明共有5个回答：西 北 西 南 西</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>2行</p>\n<p>第一行:正整数n，1≤n≤10000</p>\n<p>第二行:n个用0 1 2表示的指令</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>一个整数，小明说&ldquo;南&rdquo;的次数</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>5</p>\n<p>0 1 0 0 1</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>1</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}